H0.text: Where in the body is the cuboid bone. Ankle

H1.text: Where in the body is the cuboid bone. Wrist

H2.text: Where in the body is the cuboid bone. Elbow

H3.text: Where in the body is the cuboid bone. FOOT

A4.text: In the human body, the cuboid bone is one of the seven tarsal bones of the foot.

A5.text: The cuboid bone is the most lateral of the bones in the distal row of the tarsus.
